<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_234_r1l18"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol <expan>wıſſenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ıſt / daʒ wır vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . manig </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_234_r1l19"><expan>feltıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gerawbt vnd beſchedıgt <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein / Alſo hat vns Arnold </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_234_r1l20"><expan>Harr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> fürbracht vvıe er <expan>v̈b<ex>er</ex></expan> den <expan>görg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſchıkenhof<ex>er</ex></expan> als v̈ber </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_234_r1l21"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> geſcholln . bey eẅch ʒum <expan>Ellmpog<ex>en</ex></expan> rechts <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> vnd auch v̈ber </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_234_r1l22">Jn <expan>v<ex>er</ex>pürgt</expan> hab / Darinn ır Jm eẅr <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> <expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> beweıſet habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_234_r1l23">des wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſſ <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> / Nu ſchıken wır den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_234_r1l24"><expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> Arnold <expan>Harr<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd ettlıch <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gegenw<ex>er</ex>tıgen</expan> ʒu eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_234_r1l25">den wır befolhen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>nachʒukome<ex>n</ex></expan> . Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_234_r1l26"><expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ . <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>bottſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> aber </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_234_r1l27">
<del rend="strikethrough">fur </del> vmb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ın den <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> aber <expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gewege<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒuſein </ab>
