<pb facs="#facs_235" id="116v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_235_r1l1">möcht <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> vns dıe ʒu <expan>brıng<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>alſu<ex>er</ex>re</expan> eẅch das <expan>füklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſey / Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_235_r1l2">wellet vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darinne . <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> vnd guten <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> be </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_235_r1l3">weıſen . als wır eẅch <expan>ſunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wol getrawen / vnd eẅch vnd den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_235_r1l4">bey vns auch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun wolten . das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır vmb eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc </ab>
